<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>New Contact Form Received</title>
  <style>
    @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@400;600&display=swap');
    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background-color: #f4f4f4;
      font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
      color: #333;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 30px auto;
      padding: 30px;
      background-color: #fff;
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
    }
    h1 {
      color: #4CAF50;
      text-align: center;
    }
    p {
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .info-block {
      background-color: #fafafa;
      border-left: 4px solid #4CAF50;
      padding: 20px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .info-block p {
      margin: 8px 0;
    }
    footer {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #999;
      margin-top: 40px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>New Contact Form Received</h1>

    <p>Youâ€™ve received a new contact form submission. Details are below:</p>

    <div class="info-block">
      <p><strong>Name:</strong> {{name}}</p>
      <p><strong>Email:</strong> {{email}}</p>
      <p><strong>Contact Number:</strong> {{contactNumber}}</p>
      <p><strong>Session Date & Time:</strong> {{sessionDateTime}}</p>
      <p><strong>Session Length:</strong> {{sessionLength}}</p>
      <p><strong>Experience Level:</strong> {{experienceLevel}}</p>
      <p><strong>Identity:</strong> {{identity}}</p>
      <p><strong>Interests:</strong> {{interests}}</p>
      <p><strong>Hard Limits:</strong> {{hardLimits}}</p>
      <p><strong>Health Concerns:</strong> {{healthConcerns}}</p>
      <p><strong>Recent Reference:</strong> {{recentReference}}</p>
    </div>

    <p>Please follow up with this person as appropriate.</p>

    <footer>
      <p>&copy; {{year}} Your Business. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
